{"tid":989631,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"全球最萌狗狗離世！摯友病逝BOO「心碎」 終年13歲","createTime":"2019-01-21T04:15:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-21T05:34:20.000Z","uid":32511,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0e6d676dfebc5f3f6874018b5d98c949ad6a7630","tid":989631,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T04:15:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xF35EeA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxF35EeA.png&h=5da79615&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/huVS3Gg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhuVS3Gg.png&h=e17f58d0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/j3ZHGsX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj3ZHGsX.png&h=453629e8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WJ5S3Gi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWJ5S3Gi.png&h=76723c42&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2UkoqUE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2UkoqUE.png&h=ace13453&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n被譽為「全球最可愛狗狗」的網紅博美狗「Boo」，在臉書粉絲專頁上有1661.9萬名粉絲追蹤，今天傳出因心臟病病逝消息，終年13歲。媒體報導，牠在另一隻狗狗好友「Buddy」 於2017年過世後也生病，牠的飼主在臉書發聲明，牠一直有心臟問題，「牠的心真的碎了」，並表示牠在睡眠中安詳過世，現在已在天上與好友Buddy重新聚首。<br />\n <br />\nBoo住在美國舊金山，由主人J.H. Lee飼養，牠與拍檔Buddy靠著怎麼拍怎麼萌的可愛模樣在網路上爆紅，主人曾透露Buddy在13年前成為他們家的新一份子，此後牠們幾乎形影不離，Boo如果沒有Buddy絕對不拍照，名副其實是陪伴一生的摯友。狗主人曾在2011、2012年為牠出書，分別是《Boo全世界最可愛的狗狗》與《Boo可愛「小布」的都市生活大冒險》。<br />\n <br />\n牠的飼主今天在臉書表示：「我以深刻的哀傷心情與大家分享這件事，Boo今天早上在睡眠中離開我們，與牠最好的朋友Buddy重聚了。我們的家人都心碎了，但知道牠不再感覺痛苦或不適，讓我們感覺些許安慰。我們知道Buddy會在彩虹橋的另一端第一個迎接牠。」主人並指出Boo因為太想念好友而生病，「Boo出現心臟病的症狀，我們認為牠在Buddy離開我們時，真的心碎了。牠撐著多給了我們超過一年的時間，但現在看來牠的時候到了<br />\n，我確信對於牠們，能在天堂看見彼此將會是最快樂的時刻」。"},{"pid":"762b0feb8bcf7dd8b8cd3e9d9ed2c7bfda8f2a38","tid":989631,"uid":152123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T05:27:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92fabc7fd3d96a2e51188d30b93736a6eafe28a2","tid":989631,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T05:30:51.000Z","msg":"世上最可愛松鼠狗Boo睡夢中離世　享年13歲<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/988848\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/988848</a>"},{"pid":"d0141c3b8d0676a0f23f8b5a3aec5858c70f188b","tid":989631,"uid":2404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T05:31:45.000Z","msg":"神仙都企唔穩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e13173fdbf429d8b23550e4ff40e93e1e69b41f1","tid":989631,"uid":224107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T05:34:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}